{"tid":862432,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"有冇聽過金莎依個人？","createTime":"2018-10-14T23:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:42:45.000Z","uid":186412,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f35e528aa0570a26296b56fe2b4e83e976848280","tid":862432,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/071356_fd4f8b0446a49ce0a2334b2bb37e9bd9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F071356_fd4f8b0446a49ce0a2334b2bb37e9bd9.png&h=1c2cf17e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢把聲同作詞能力都幾唔錯<br />\n唯一敗北係大陸妹<br />\n當年同林俊傑嘅一首《被風吹過的夏天》出晒名<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JbFrE_UbVyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJbFrE_UbVyI&d=o6wDr6ucdGZgXGGAOBDxVDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ad28df5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JbFrE_UbVyI</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人聽過《星月神話》，金莎作曲作詞，嗰種古風憂怨感，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dxPpC02tyUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdxPpC02tyUY&d=o6wDr6ucdGZgXGGAOBDxVDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c464326d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dxPpC02tyUY</a>"},{"pid":"03e9297d9434179656c7ad939a9ff14d37784abe","tid":862432,"uid":70301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:17:55.000Z","msg":"有聽過，同林俊傑重有一首合唱，期待愛"},{"pid":"73487e97d18e04aa19a9ab9d0c5ba27a01ed8506","tid":862432,"uid":186412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03e9297d9434179656c7ad939a9ff14d37784abe","tid":862432,"uid":70301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:17:55.000Z","msg":"有聽過，同林俊傑重有一首合唱，期待愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T23:19:46.000Z","msg":"👍🏻仲有發現愛"},{"pid":"600fe96a1c67537d78ec8e4e874b9eb970caaad5","tid":862432,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco